# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.tmp

# OpenClaw host-specific state (created when a harness is registered/run as a workspace)
.openclaw/
**/openclaw-workspace-state.json

# Per-deployment env overrides — non-secret deployment-specific values.
# Each harness ships a committed .env.example template instead.
**/.env

# Per-harness runtime ledger — ships empty, fills on the host
**/state/seen.json

# Template files OpenClaw re-scaffolds on `agents add` (not part of any harness)
**/USER.md
**/TOOLS.md
**/HEARTBEAT.md

# Internal session-state note (not part of the distributed repo)
STATUS.md

# OS noise
.DS_Store
